Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.04,0:02:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter the time, Iyona-chan always looks lovely!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.47,0:02:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I love her so much!
