Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.68,0:02:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I got so close to her! {hope}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.76,0:02:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Seaside school!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.46,0:02:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Soon enough, I'll see it - Iyona-chan's swimsuit!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.40,0:02:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.12,0:02:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it this time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.63,0:02:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, look! This newest high-leg swimsuit!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.24,0:02:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,This summer, I've decided on going audacious!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.56,0:02:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,My swimsuit would wipe the floor with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.12,0:02:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's by a famous Italian designer from Milan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.17,0:02:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Vittorio himself designed my swimsuit
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.24,0:02:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.16,0:03:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore! My looks will be unrivaled. {I won't lose to anyone - no clue}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.38,0:03:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Harako-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.89,0:03:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The privilege of wearing an unrivaled swimsuit will be mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.82,0:03:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, let's have a duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.50,0:03:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it, do it! Looks fun!
