Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.99,0:03:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.68,0:04:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,How about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.85,0:04:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna throw up when I see a male high-leg!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.05,0:04:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.63,0:04:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You've hit the bull's eye, Ijigawa! {no clue what's やるな}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.42,0:04:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It becomes you so well, Ijigawa-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.60,0:04:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.12,0:04:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oaya-sensei looks amazing too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.77,0:04:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That's our teacher, alright! {sasuga}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.52,0:04:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Ijigawa looks stunning,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.04,0:04:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,but Oaya-sensei can make you lose your head!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.78,0:04:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{?? was dohyu in manga}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.62,0:05:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, Honmaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.78,0:05:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Impressive, Iyona-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.55,0:05:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,As audacious as it gets!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.66,0:05:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,My mother said...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.88,0:05:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona-chan,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.50,0:05:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I've picked a perfect swimsuit \Nfor you to wear at seaside school.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.26,0:05:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.02,0:05:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That'd be awfully embarrassing, mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.65,0:05:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What is embarrassing about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.31,0:05:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That's exactly what your young, vivacious body needs.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.11,0:05:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's just some strings, not a swimsuit. {no clue what she means by "string; cord​"}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.52,0:05:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,As a daughter of the Kawai clan,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.25,0:05:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,how could you be embarassed in any way \Nby such a swimsuit?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.94,0:05:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,As you're being gazed at, your body is kept in tonus, 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.10,0:05:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and so you become even more beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.38,0:05:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you imagine what a stunning young maiden \Nyou'll be when you grow up?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.86,0:05:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.72,0:05:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.77,0:05:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I {\i1}am{\i0} a bad daughter, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.84,0:06:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! My normal cute swimsuit is not here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.08,0:06:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.40,0:06:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't make light of my words and get away with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.25,0:06:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us meet again after your body has learned \Nto wear this swimsuit unabashedly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.29,0:06:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.73,0:06:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,My, isn't your mother a lovely woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.59,0:06:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's fine too. It befits you greatly!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.75,0:06:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, Iyona-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.05,0:06:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't believe how good it looks on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.39,0:06:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The gazes are swarming all over me... {unsure, maybe "I can't help to twine around; to twist around; to coil around from the stares/gazes"}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.44,0:06:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It {\i1}is{\i0} too embarrassing, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.35,0:06:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona-chan, no need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.30,0:06:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll also wear a high-leg matching with yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.30,0:06:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.46,0:06:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.56,0:06:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,My high leg swimsuit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.31,0:07:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.00,0:07:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So embarrassing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.04,0:07:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish there was a hole for me to hide in! {/if there was a hole, I'd enter it}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.40,0:07:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hole?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.22,0:07:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.31,0:07:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you taking me, Taru?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.27,0:07:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,To where I was playing in the sand earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.63,0:07:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.34,0:07:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you doing that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.10,0:07:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru hid inside a hole!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.39,0:07:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.86,0:07:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a saying for when you're embarrassed - \N"I wish there was a hole for me to hide in!"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.92,0:07:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, why you embarrassed?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.96,0:07:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,'Cause my pants went bust \Nand my willy was on display for everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.90,0:07:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, dear ladies.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.91,0:07:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,How about you leave behind the willy-displaying idiot \Nand join me for a swim?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.22,0:07:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Harako too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.14,0:08:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I got pants! Pants! {unsure}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.10,0:08:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.81,0:08:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Harako embarrassed too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.84,0:08:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn right I {\i1}am{\i0} embarrassed!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.09,0:08:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it back right now! {guess}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.58,0:08:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone laughing! This seems pretty fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.12,0:08:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,On display!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.56,0:08:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.12,0:08:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,One more.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.41,0:08:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No! No! Please stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.58,0:08:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Jabao too, Korekiyo too! Everyone embarrassed!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.11,0:08:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.20,0:08:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Trunsform...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.92,0:08:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.38,0:08:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Get back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.21,0:08:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop, Taruruuto!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.55,0:08:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! Let's catch him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.36,0:08:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This - Smooth Mermaiding-kun. {no pun originally as well, suisui ningyo-kun}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.42,0:09:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Wearing this, you can swim as fast as as fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.59,0:09:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.42,0:09:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.18,0:09:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Try to catch! I'm here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.15,0:09:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You prick!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.44,0:09:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Get back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.79,0:09:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll get you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.93,0:09:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.41,0:09:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! {kinda hear some "nazu" from jabao there?}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.84,0:09:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.34,0:09:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that dangerous?! {guss, not in manga}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.84,0:09:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm exhausted... {yarareta}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.42,0:09:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,True...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.45,0:09:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,On display!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.27,0:10:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru sure knows how to make a show of it. {showy; loud; flashy; gaudy​}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.91,0:10:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope he doesn't regret it when he's scolded later.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.73,0:10:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.02,0:10:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.60,0:10:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for what you did for me earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.55,0:10:59.94,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H198517&}The risqué swimsuit shines brightly {きわどい水着がまぶしく輝いて}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.94,0:11:05.77,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H198517&}I'm all jittery today, on this white sand beach {ジリジリしちゃうぜ 白い砂の上}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.14,0:11:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Whaa...{g}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.41,0:11:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Weirdos!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.77,0:11:12.71,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H198517&}Hold the board in your right hand \Nand smash the accelerator of your heart {右手にボードをかかえハートのアクセル全開}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.71,0:11:16.50,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H198517&}Toot-toot! Let's go to the surfing beach! {Fu~ Fu~ 行こうよサーフィンビーチ}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.01,0:11:25.42,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H198517&}Your gaze lingers on my white bare skin {アナタの視線が 素肌にからみつく}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.42,0:11:31.21,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H198517&}My heart palpitates wildly in the orange sunlight {ドキドキしちゃうわ オレンジの陽射し}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.21,0:11:34.62,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H198517&}We would carefully decide on sunglasses, {小意気にグラサンきめて}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.62,0:11:38.18,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H198517&}So raise that volume on the radio {レディオのボリュームあげて}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.18,0:11:42.78,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H198517&}Toot-toot! Wait for me, surfing beach! {Fu~ Fu~ 待ってよサーフィンビーチ}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.93,0:11:49.77,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H198517&}The sea in midsummer is full of excitement! {真夏の海はワクワクいっぱい}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.66,0:11:57.20,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H198517&}And I'm aiming for a thrill, like what they have in movies... {映画のようなスリルをめざし・・・}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.09,0:12:03.45,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H198517&}This sun in a big blue sky \NIs burning brightly {青空の太陽 ぎらぎら燃えて}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.78,0:12:03.45,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\an1\3c&H7247B2&}Woo, if it's for you... {anatanara~}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.40,0:12:10.35,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H198517&}The sublime vacation, feeling better than ever! {とびきりVacation 気分は最高!}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.20,0:12:09.43,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\an1\3c&H7247B2&}Woo, forever and ever...{itsudemo~}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.35,0:12:15.98,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H198517&}Let's make some splashes, then scuttle away! {水しぶきあげて 駆け出そうよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.30,0:12:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.35,0:12:15.98,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\an1\3c&H7247B2&}Woo, gladly! {OK yo}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.84,0:12:21.05,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H198517&}This earth is only ours! {地球はオレたちのものさ!!}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.84,0:12:21.05,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\an1\3c&H7247B2&}This earth is yours! {地球はアナタのものよ!!}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.13,0:12:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, everyone, let's do some special surfing today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.51,0:12:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Any volunteers? {applicant; candidate; person interested in doing something; person wanting to do something; interested party; voluntee}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.33,0:12:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,No, thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.67,0:12:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, teacher! I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.77,0:12:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona-chan is coming along, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.26,0:12:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.81,0:13:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona-san, if you'd like it, I would gladly teach you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.36,0:13:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Beautiful teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.30,0:13:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,With consideration to my prior abilities,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.07,0:13:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe I should be entrusted with coaching the female group.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.36,0:13:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, for someone retaining the \NWorld Junior Surfer Champion title for five years straight,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.54,0:13:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,there's no need to be showing off. {affectation; showing off; putting on an air; appearances; doing something just for show​}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.88,0:13:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well. Please do just that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.24,0:13:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, among those who remain, \Nanyone would like to enjoy riding with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.70,0:13:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn this prick Harako! \NWe let him look so cool before Iyona-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.28,0:13:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Me tired. Can't hold buckets any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.37,0:13:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! If Taru's with us, we can work something out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.13,0:13:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.14,0:13:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher! I'll do that too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.12,0:13:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-kun, do you have any surfing experience?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.74,0:13:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No... But I have a feeling \Nthat something good may come out of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.68,0:13:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Admirable! Athletes who constantly look \Nto challenge themselves - now that's what I love!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.33,0:13:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher, also me and this guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.72,0:13:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? I'm fine enough here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.90,0:14:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, everyone. I'm counting on you to train intensely.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.70,0:14:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.32,0:14:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Counting on you, Taru!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.08,0:14:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all the basics, \Nyou'll have to memorize the rest on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.78,0:14:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, who wants to start?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.20,0:14:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Start, like there?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.19,0:14:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean, in that sea?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.24,0:14:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. Isn't it perfectly rough? {guess}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.51,0:14:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't be serious! \NYou're asking for too much, teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.25,0:14:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what's up with everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.76,0:14:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Jabao-kun, maybe you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.36,0:14:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You want me to do it? To tell you the truth, I have second thoughts about this, so I'd rather do it later. {reserved; shy; timid}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.09,0:14:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Quacking in your boots, Jabao?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.42,0:14:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Are you calling me a coward or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.83,0:14:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I wrong for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.68,0:14:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! Courageous boy Jaba Jabao \Nwill show you what's what.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.96,0:14:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, come, Korekiyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.62,0:14:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as you said, I have \Nsome second thoughts about this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.48,0:15:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Like it or not, we're in the same boat! {sharing one's lot with another; being in the same boat}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.34,0:15:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Now come!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.60,0:15:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Jabao-san, please let go of my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.94,0:15:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Last warning to everyone, don't come near that ocean! {guess}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.15,0:15:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's deadly. {guess}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.04,0:15:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,How trifling.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.38,0:15:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher, I suggest we leave those cowards on the shore \Nand have me riding alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.02,0:15:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a skillful getting out. \NDo it in the same fashion, everyone! {unsure if it's not some special surfing term}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.19,0:16:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Impressive!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.13,0:16:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't he cool, Iyona-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.38,0:16:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.56,0:16:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never be able to do it in the same fashion!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.94,0:16:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I'll have to rely on Taru, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.28,0:16:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Taru...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.00,0:16:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.44,0:16:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you use some magic to enable me to surf?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.37,0:16:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, that impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.34,0:16:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Me don't know surfing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.66,0:16:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't be talking like that, \Njust help me out a bit, Taruruuto!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.53,0:16:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.91,0:16:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I know! I should ask Tama-chan \Nfor everything I don't understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.82,0:16:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.36,0:16:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But I remembered I left Tama-chan behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.70,0:16:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-kun, let's do it while supporting each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.34,0:16:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You can count on me, Iyona-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.95,0:17:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, nothing is impossible for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.14,0:17:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, Honmaru-sama, let me accompany you \Nto where the waves are!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.92,0:17:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.01,0:17:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, do your best! I'll be rooting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.79,0:17:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not what I meant...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.72,0:17:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Now! Iyona-chan, you come too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.92,0:17:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.93,0:17:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your best, Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.48,0:17:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.53,0:17:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd sooner die on these waves!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.89,0:17:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, stay strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.94,0:17:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We're riding for real this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.72,0:17:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Taru's magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.05,0:17:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.02,0:17:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, Honmaru, get up! \NAnd I'll be sure to hold your legs up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.58,0:17:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.97,0:17:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it, let's start, Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.06,0:18:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Been a while since I could roam waves freely! {unsure}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.15,0:18:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,After me! {guess}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.32,0:18:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What just...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.58,0:18:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.78,0:18:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,How is he able to surf in the opposite direction?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.17,0:18:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Just what I expected from Honmaru-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.48,0:18:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,He had known long ago everything I was teaching them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.68,0:18:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.63,0:18:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,He's riding better than professionals!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.68,0:18:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.71,0:18:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,He even nailed the loop \Nthat's said to be every surfer's dream? {again, no clue bc surfing term?}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.99,0:18:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,A piece of cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.62,0:19:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad for you, Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.70,0:19:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Taru!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.12,0:19:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's coming... {geuess}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.63,0:19:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. No doubt about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.12,0:19:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,This tide, this wind... {guess, no clue what's this kiyassu, prolly some surfing term?}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.40,0:19:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,A perfect sibling synergy that only \Ncomes together once every 20 years...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.63,0:19:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We were waiting dormant for long enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.40,0:19:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Giant Swell is finally here! {"Swell - the energy powered by strong winds that produce wave trains;" - nothing else sounds similar to whatever they say}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.48,0:19:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Giant Swell?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.67,0:19:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Young man! You seem to know your way around surfing,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.52,0:19:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,but you shouldn't even think about riding those waters.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.81,0:19:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, those waves are a brutal beast indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.93,0:19:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,If you value your life, don't come near it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.86,0:20:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that sure sounds like fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.81,0:20:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Ain't it, Honmaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.82,0:20:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we also try our prowess \Nagainst that Giant Swell thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.95,0:20:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! A combination such as us two \Ncan get anything done!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.21,0:20:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.90,0:20:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do it! {guess}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.73,0:20:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,We were once in that age too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.77,0:20:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.13,0:20:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, are we going too?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.14,0:20:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.74,0:20:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The overturning pace is getting somehow strange...{no clue}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.61,0:20:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys, it's about time we returned ashore.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.48,0:20:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Harako, some phenomenal waves are coming soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.04,0:20:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna try to ride them with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.97,0:20:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Curious! I accept that duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.48,0:20:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's dangerous! Stop while you can, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.02,0:20:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep going!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.27,0:20:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.86,0:21:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do it, Harako!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.36,0:21:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't lose, Honmaru! \NAin't no way I'll let you look all cool and manly!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.79,0:21:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you guys quite experienced in this? {/good in this}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.94,0:21:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Get ready to see just how experienced we are!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.88,0:21:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.30,0:21:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Harako, now's your time to quit \Nif you don't wanna end like them! {guess}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.78,0:21:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you look down on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.60,0:21:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,He's also pretty determined, \Nisn't he, Surfboard-kun? {guess, no clue what's this ijippai}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.70,0:21:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.85,0:21:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,My magic ran its ten minute course!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.09,0:21:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh? Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.40,0:21:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And how am I supposed to come back from here, Taru?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.13,0:21:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot, don't come near! {guess}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.83,0:21:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, you're lucky that neither of you got seriously injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.92,0:21:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,This means you'll be able to enter \Nthe long-distance swimming contest tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.64,0:22:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Long-distance? But do they specify \Njust for how long we'll have to swim?{no clue why he cares}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.16,0:22:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, Honmaru! We'll settle the score \Nfor surfing with {long-distance }swimming tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.55,0:22:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,This!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.57,0:22:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay! Won! Won again!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.81,0:22:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit! Taru, let's have one more round! {/duel}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.56,0:22:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure! As many as you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.36,0:22:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll do it! I'm locked and loaded, Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.51,0:22:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.37,0:22:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the final day of the fun seaside school adventure!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.53,0:22:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll hold a test of courage tonight! {test of courage (by going to a frightening place, e.g. a graveyard)}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.15,0:22:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,After taking a bath, me and Iyona-chan \Ngo out to the beach at night...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.35,0:22:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you big time, Taruruuto!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.83,0:22:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, what's courage test?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.81,0:23:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Magical Taruruuto-kun: \NExhausting Test of Courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.29,0:23:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Ghost...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.29,0:23:06.55,Sign,,0,0,0,,Episode 48\NExhausting Test of Courage {ヘトヘト肝だめし}
